    "Name": "Haruna HAR-101",
    "Details": "The HAR-101 is a Capellan experimental design commissioned by Sun Tzu Liao, blending mixed Inner Sphere and Clan technology into a fast close-range harasser. Stealth armor powered by an ECM suite and MASC pushing the 35-ton frame past 170 kph make it extremely difficult to engage reliably. A Vibroblade, twin Streak SRM 2s and a Heavy Medium Laser give it genuine bite once it closes, while an Active Probe rounds out the electronics suite.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Nimble</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>",
